About Us
.entry-header
.entry-header-wrapper
A local favorite since 2003…
We prioritize fast, friendly service, great food, and cold AC! We’ve always got your game on one of our 19 big-screen TVs.
We have the best homestyle comfort favorites and don’t forget our famous tater tots! Take a seat at a booth or the bar, relax and catch a game.
Because of our location at a relatively high elevation on the island, Jack Flats stays open for as long as possible during hurricanes. Hurricanes are part of life in Key West, and we are proud to serve the community when life on the island gets a little messy, as it did during Hurricane Irma of 2017. We are proud Conchs and continual sponsors of local youth sports.
